in cycle i will create a class for each player for the following: 1. movement 2. trail 3. collisions 4.the player 5. trail collisions 6. player wins 7. cycle color change 8. trail color change 
after that there will be the gameover class in which it will command the color change, and the player wins class to display the final winner and etc.